Quickstrike:




Quickstrike gave Black Arachnia one last look, sorry he was occupied with 
the mouse than getting the chance to talk to her again after a time of 
hatred. He walked backwards from the door, then ran at it, leaping up and 
kicking it. He did it two more times. He paused, looking at the closed door. 
Then something logic clicked in his brain.

Computer dummy! he brain shouted at him.

He looked up and commanded the computer, "Computer, open the door where unit 
Transulas is!" It took a second or two, then the door slid open. The Fuzor's 
eyes lit up with anger as he saw Transulas leaning over to Dark Mouse. He 
ran inside, as fast as he could, and braced himself as he rammed into the 
spider as hard as he could. For some reason, he was destined to stop him 
from killing her.
